%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
%% docs/design.md §9.1 - registration flow (as-built).
%% Asymmetric: only agents call the broker; broker NEVER initiates.
%% Regenerate the PNG with: mmdc -i registration.mmd -o registration-flow.png
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CAg as Consumer<br/>Agent
    participant PAg as Provider<br/>Agent
    participant Bk  as Broker<br/>(central)

    Note over PAg: snapshot local nodes →<br/>allocatable + topology
    PAg->>Bk: POST /api/v1/advertisements<br/>(mTLS, every 30 s,<br/>doubles as heartbeat)
    Note right of Bk: ClusterAdvertisement CR<br/>upserted.<br/>ClusterAdvertisementReconciler<br/>flips Status.Available=true
    Bk-->>PAg: 200 + piggybacked instructions<br/>(currently ignored, the 5 s poll<br/>is the dispatch path)

    CAg->>Bk: POST /api/v1/heartbeat<br/>(mTLS, every 15 s,<br/>carries placement policy +<br/>discovered location + measured RTTs)
    Note right of Bk: in-memory ConsumerRegistry<br/>upsert lastSeen + liqoClusterId<br/>+ policy + coordinates
    Bk-->>CAg: 200

    Note over PAg,CAg: Both agents now poll<br/>GET /api/v1/instructions every 5 s
    PAg->>Bk: GET /api/v1/instructions
    Bk-->>PAg: [] (no instructions until a Reservation lands)
    CAg->>Bk: GET /api/v1/instructions
    Bk-->>CAg: []
